### What’s next

If you want to know if your website is using eco-friendly web hosting, you can enter your domain into the [Green Web Check](https://www.thegreenwebfoundation.org/green-web-check/). If your site is using a green host and you are using a .eco domain name, you can add a badge to your [.eco profile](https://profiles.eco/profile/certification/green-web-check) showing that. [Here’s how to do it](/news/green-web-check-ecolabel/).

If your site isn’t using an eco-friendly host, check out our [post on eco-friendly domain retailers](https://go.eco/news/finding-a-green-domain-retailer/) - they also offer web hosting services.

Let’s work together to achieve a **fossil-fuel free Internet by 2030**. Choosing a sustainable web hosting provider is a great place to start.
